==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sensitize
<hw>Sen"si*tize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Photog.)</fld>
<def>To render sensitive, or susceptible of being easily acted on by the
actinic rays of the sun; <as>as, <ex>sensitized</ex> paper or
plate</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sensitizer</ent>⟦br⟧
